  <travelInformation><![CDATA[<p>All our holidays include return travel to resort either by flight or train and then the transfer between the airport or railway station.</p>
<p>All departures are on Saturdays with stays for 7 or 14 nights.</p>
<p>The transfer in La Plagne will stop as close as possible to your chosen accommodation. In some cases, there may be a couple of minutes' walk due to regulations on where coaches can stop. </p>
<p>Private transfers and self-drive are available.</p>]]></travelInformation>
